-- India May Lift Restrictions on Foreign Mining Ventures, Express Reports
-- Victoria Batchelor
-- 2010-06-24T00:29:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-24/india-may-lift-restrictions-on-foreign-mining-ventures-express-reports.html

          
          
             India’s government is planning to 
remove a ban on foreign mining companies having several joint 
ventures to mine the same mineral in the nation, the Financial 
Express reported, citing government officials it didn’t 
identify.  
          
          


  


        